Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Jacky Rosen
email: info@durbinforsenate.com
subject: Your $5 will have an immediate impact
body: Peter, I just have to ask one more time: Can you split $5 between my campaignand Dick Durbin to keep Nevada and the Senate blue?[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?amount=5] SPLIT $5NOW → [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?amount=5] It'sno exaggeration to say that reaching our fundraising goal will determine whathappens on Election Day. That's because dark money donors have poured $75million into Nevada to defeat me – and now, a new poll was released that showsme TIED with my far-right opponent . The only way I can fight back and pullahead is with your support. I know it may not sound like much, but it’sgrassroots supporters like you giving $5 or $25 at a time who can truly make acritical difference in this battleground race – not political experts orbillionaire megadonors. That’s why it’s so important we all do our part. Butright now, we’re still very short of our goal to raise $1,000,000 beforeElection Day: So please, can you split $5 between my campaign and Dick Durbinto help me reach my fundraising goal and defend our Senate majority?[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?amount=5] If you'vesaved your payment information with ActBlue Express, your donation will gothrough immediately and be split between Jacky Rosen and Dick Durbin: CHIP IN$5 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?express_lane=true&amount;=5]CHIP IN $25 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?express_lane=true&amount;=25]CHIP IN $50 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?express_lane=true&amount;=50]CHIP IN $100 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?express_lane=true&amount;=100]CHIP IN $200 →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split?express_lane=true&amount;=200]CHIP IN OTHER AMOUNT →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_dd_fr_rosen_split] Thank you for youressential support, Peter.
